      "metadata": {
        "title": "Bumble Dating App: Meet & Date",
        "subtitle": "Find new people & chat singles",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "Bumble is the women-first dating app designed to create safer, more respectful connections and conversations that lead to better in-person dates and relationships.\n\nHOW WE SUPPORT YOUR DATING JOURNEY\nWe empower you to show up as your most authentic self, so you can move confidently toward meeting in real life by:\n- Focusing on you as a person, not a profile. When you write your bio and prompts, or update your photos, we\u2019ll share personalized tips that help highlight the unique qualities that make you stand out.\n- Showing you people who match your energy. Just set your Intentions and Looking For to find people who want to date the way you do. Or, add Interest Badges to find people who are into what you\u2019re into.\n- Empowering women to message first. Once a match is made, women send the first chat, and their match has 24 hours to reply before the connection expires.\n- Prioritizing safety at every step of your dating journey. Get ID Verified early-on (like the majority of our community), try Share Date to drop location details with the group chat, or use Block and Report, Unmatch, or the Safety Center for extra support.\n- Giving your chats a boost. Our built-in guidance helps keep your exchanges kind and respectful, while chat and video options make it easier to progress your connection, without ever leaving the app.\n- Adapting to your needs. If you want to take a step back from meeting new people, enable Snooze Mode to take a break from dating without losing your current matches.\n\nLooking for even more options? Try Bumble Boost, Bumble Premium, and Premium+. Bumble is free, but these premium services give you even more flexibility and dating options, with advanced filters, extended matches, Incognito Mode, and Travel Mode.\n\nADDITIONAL INFO\nYour personal data is securely processed in line with our privacy policy and applicable laws.\n\nSupport: https://bumble.com/contact\nTerms of Service: https://bumble.com/en/terms\nPrivacy: https://bumble.com/en/privacy\n\nBumble Inc. is the parent company of Bumble, Badoo, and BFF.",
